1
00:01:19,960 --> 00:01:22,760
Why did you bring up his name?

2
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:23,720
Do you know him?

3
00:01:24,520 --> 00:01:25,320
No.

4
00:01:27,039 --> 00:01:28,800
Back at the cabin on the mountain,

5
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:31,840
you called his name while you were out with a fever.

6
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:40,479
He's very important to you.

7
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:46,039
Very important.

8
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:51,600
But please keep this a secret.

9
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:54,280
Don't mention Jiujiu's name to anyone.

10
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,200
How important?

11
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,720
Is he the one you love?

12
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:08,320
He and I don't have that kind of relationship.

13
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:11,320
But regarding his affairs,

14
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:12,320
I can't say much.

15
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,160
When I find him,

16
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:15,220
if you want to know,

17
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,200
you can ask him yourself.

18
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:21,520
You have to treat Chuyun

19
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,920
and run the medical hall.

20
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,970
Do you have time to look for him?

21
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:29,880
I'm free anyway.

22
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:31,680
Since I already know about this,

23
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:33,680
I can help you out.

24
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,320
No need.

25
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:40,040
If you're really that free,

26
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,900
you might as well be my assistant.

27
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:46,040
Then teach me about the Jianghu.

28
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,000
For example, tell me

29
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,800
where to find Baixiaosheng

30
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,200
or other know-it-alls.

31
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:53,400
Didn't I tell you those are all scams?

32
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:55,960
I still want to understand the Jianghu.

33
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:58,360
It'll make traveling easier in the future.

34
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,880
And once I know more,

35
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:01,540
maybe I can actually help you.

36
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:06,200
When I went to the Ghost Market to send a letter today,

37
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:09,400
I did meet someone claiming to be a know-it-all.

38
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:14,040
But I don't know if he's reliable.

39
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:17,640
We won't know until we try.

40
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,440
I'll take you back to the medical hall first,

41
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:24,240
then go to the Ghost Market to see if that know-it-all is still there.

42
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:26,440
Get on.

43
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,440
Thank you.

44
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,360
Hey.

45
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,480
Brother Shen, Doctor Ji.

46
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,380
You two haven't slept yet.

47
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:42,120
Neither have you.

48
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:45,320
You came out of a girl's room in the middle of the night.

49
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:47,680
I went to check on Miss Chuyun.

50
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:49,640
Young Master Du.

51
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:52,000
Why do you still have that worm?

52
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:58,040
I thought I could use it for treatment.

53
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,320
Treatment?

54
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,360
Yes. My family has a secret remedy.

55
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:05,650
It uses this Heart-eating Worm to stimulate the nerves,

56
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:08,680
which can wake someone from a coma.

57
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:10,720
Lately,

58
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:12,980
I saw Miss Chuyun wasn't getting better.

59
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,440
I was getting worried,

60
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,570
so I wanted to try it.

61
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:17,720
Indeed.

62
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,320
The storybooks say

63
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:20,279
poisonous worms can kill people,

64
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:21,279
but they can also heal.

65
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,720
They are quite magical.

66
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:25,920
Brother Shen.

67
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:28,280
I saw you carrying Doctor Ji back.

68
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,680
Is she injured?

69
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:32,560
No, she just sprained her ankle.

70
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:33,880
It's hard for her to walk.

71
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:35,040
Do you need my help?

72
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:37,840
No need. We can handle it ourselves.

73
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,159
"We"?

74
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:42,080
If I may ask,

75
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:44,360
are you two a couple?

76
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,520
No.

77
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,760
By the way, Mr. Du,

78
00:04:56,760 --> 00:05:00,560
it's quite novel how you use poisonous insects to treat illnesses.

79
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:02,720
Could you tell me more about it?

80
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,800
Another time, perhaps.

81
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,360
I have some things to attend to.

82
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,620
I'll take my leave now.

83
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:18,280
Alright, let me walk you back to your room first.

84
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:20,740
Or the Ghost Market will be gone by daybreak.

85
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:35,520
Which medicine is for bruises and injuries?

86
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:36,850
Just bring the box over.

87
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,760
Go ahead if you're busy.

88
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:54,140
The Ghost Market will close soon.

89
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:55,560
Alright.

90
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,480
Your injury isn't serious anyway.

91
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,280
I'm off.

92
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,560
Wait.

93
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,360
The Ghost Market has its rules.

94
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,520
Be careful.

95
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:10,360
The Know-it-all should be at the east end of the Ghost Market.

96
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,360
Poisonous insects.

97
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:33,040
To cure the illness.

98
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:44,600
Isn't this the morning grocery market?

99
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,280
You swindler!

100
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,760
I've been looking for you for a long time.

101
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,360
You came here to scam people.

102
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:09,880
Young man,

103
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,120
do you have the wrong person?

104
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:13,320
I am no swindler.

105
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:16,000
I am famous in this Ghost Market.

106
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:19,160
Wrong person? I'd recognize you even if you turned to ash.

107
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:22,360
You cheated me out of all my travel expenses on Long Street.

108
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,480
That wasn't a scam.

109
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:26,040
I really am the Know-it-all.

110
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:28,720
I told you to come here to find the Know-it-all,

111
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,380
but you came at the wrong time.

112
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:31,700
During the day,

113
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,360
we're not open.

114
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,760
Do you take me for a three-year-old child?

115
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,560
Come with me to the authorities.

116
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:39,640
Not at all.

117
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,560
During the day, I sell books.

118
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:44,490
I only trade information at night.

119
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:47,400
Dare to toy with me?

120
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:50,480
I usually sell information here,

121
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:52,540
and I've offended quite a few people.

122
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:55,210
There are too many prying eyes during the day.

123
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,120
The title of Know-it-all

124
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,850
is something I dare not reveal.

125
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:03,360
Don't hit me. As compensation,

126
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,260
I won't charge you any silver.

127
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:07,680
Speak.

128
00:08:08,200 --> 00:08:10,000
What information do you want?

129
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,480
I heard that fifteen years ago,

130
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:21,240
a mother and son from out of town came here.

131
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:25,400
That is true.

132
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:28,760
Sitai Town is remote and hard to find.

133
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:31,440
Few outsiders can get in.

134
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:34,360
The mother and son lived here for a few days,

135
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:36,720
but since the locals were hostile to outsiders back then,

136
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,280
they moved away.

137
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:41,080
Moved away? Do you know where they went?

138
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,039
That's their private business.

139
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:43,970
How would I know?

140
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:46,540
They aren't from the martial arts world.

141
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,280
Then do you know

142
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:51,520
who originally lived in the Yan Family Escort Agency?

143
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:52,920
I don't know.

144
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:53,720
You don't know anything?

145
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,180
Aren't you a know-it-all?

146
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:00,080
I'll spare you this time.

147
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,320
If there is a next time,

148
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,920
you won't let me off lightly.

149
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,920
I won't dare do it again.

150
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:12,800
By the way,

151
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:15,920
how old is that child now?

152
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,200
Well...

153
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:21,280
I remember the child was

154
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,080
about

155
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:24,250
five or six years old back then.

156
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,720
By my count,

157
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,250
he must be about twenty now.

158
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:42,120
This kid has quite a temper.

159
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:48,320
Miss Chen, let's talk this over calmly.

160
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,480
What are you doing?

161
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:51,620
How dare you betray Adoptive Father.

162
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,440
Don't even think about hurting him.

163
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,520
It fell right into my lap.

164
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:05,920
Your Highness,

165
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:08,760
I'm taking your life today.

166
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:10,260
Your Highness.

167
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,700
This kid not only has a bad temper,

168
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,770
but he's actually got some skills.

169
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:37,960
My money tree.

170
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,600
I must explain today's matter

171
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:46,160
clearly to My Lord.

172
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,280
Adoptive Father.

173
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:04,360
Baishitong actually dared to betray you

174
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:06,880
and pass news to the Heir of King Zhenbei.

175
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,900
In our line of work,

176
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,360
money is king.

177
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:12,040
Who would say no to money?

178
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:14,480
Besides, the work I do

179
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,120
is to serve friends in the martial arts world

180
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:18,050
by passing news and intelligence.

181
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,080
Li'er.

182
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:20,880
You are so willful.

183
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:23,210
Apologize to the gentleman properly.

184
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,280
I was impulsive.

185
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:30,560
I offended you, Sir.

186
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,640
Please forgive me.

187
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:35,000
Think nothing of it.

188
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:37,320
Li'er,

189
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:38,360
you acted on your own

190
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,960
and nearly caused a disaster.

191
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,960
Go back and accept your punishment.

192
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:47,600
What did he ask you?

193
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:49,880
No...

194
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:52,120
what did he ask me again?

195
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,360
Li'er.

196
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,600
He asked me about

197
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:06,420
the whereabouts of General Shen and his mother from years ago.

198
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,480
Thank you for the news, Sir.

199
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:17,760
Don't tell anyone about this.

200
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:20,520
Consider it done.

201
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:23,560
Thank you, Chief Escort Yan.

202
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:25,360
I will take my leave now.

203
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:31,960
Father.

204
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:35,620
If the Heir is truly the descendant of General Shen,

205
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:40,080
why would he investigate his own whereabouts?

206
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,320
[Sighs]

207
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:55,520
What are you doing?

208
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:56,400
Don't worry.

209
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,280
I've weakened the toxicity significantly.

210
00:12:58,280 --> 00:13:00,140
Even if we can't cure her illness,

211
00:13:00,280 --> 00:13:01,920
it won't hurt her.

212
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:12,040
Be careful. You aren't sick.

213
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:13,760
If it bites you,

214
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,130
you'll be poisoned.

215
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,120
Ji Bai.

216
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:56,840
Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

217
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,080
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

218
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:57,720
Xiao Xiaoxue, Yi Yinan.

219
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:58,840
Xiao Xiaoxue, Yi, Yi, Nan.

220
00:13:58,840 --> 00:13:59,640
Xiao Xiaoxue.

221
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:27,080
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

222
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:32,120
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

223
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:32,120
Pan Xiulong.

224
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:32,600
Lyu, Sun, Zhang.

225
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,800
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

226
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,800
Pan Xiulong.
